# Vendored, third-party browser libraries are committed verbatim (offline-first).
# Mark them so they don't pollute PR diffs or GitHub's language statistics.
# `linguist-vendored` -> excluded from language stats and flagged as vendored.
# `-diff`             -> git shows "Binary files differ" instead of a huge diff.
skills/codevista/scripts/viewer/vendor/*.js   linguist-vendored -diff
skills/codevista/scripts/viewer/vendor/*.mjs  linguist-vendored -diff
